《'''金钱陷阱'''》（{{lang-en|The Money Pit}}）是1986年上映的美国[[喜劇電影|喜劇電影]]，由{{tsl|en|Richard Benjamin|理查德·本杰明|}}执导，[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]和{{tsl|en|Shelley Long|雪莱·朗|}}主演。影片讲述的是一对夫妇试图翻修最近购买的房子。该片在[[纽约|纽约]]和{{tsl|en|Lattingtown, New York|拉汀镇|}}拍摄，由[[斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格|斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格]]联合执行制片。这部电影是对[[加里·格兰特|加里·格兰特]]1948年的喜剧《{{tsl|en|Mr. Blandings Builds His Dream House|燕雀香巢|}}》的翻拍。<ref>{{cite web|last=Dean|first=Rob|url=https://news.avclub.com/remembering-the-money-pit-on-its-30th-anniversary-1798245776/amp|title=Remembering The Money Pit on its 30th anniversary|publisher=AV Club|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2020-05-14|archive-date=2019-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706013713/https://news.avclub.com/remembering-the-money-pit-on-its-30th-anniversary-1798245776/amp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年，美国[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]](NBC)宣布将根据这部电影拍摄一部电视剧，<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=https://www.deadline.com/2013/10/nbc-developing-comedy-based-on-movie-the-money-pit-with-justin-spitzer-amblin/ |title=NBC Developing Comedy Based On Movie ‘The Money Pit’ With Justin Spitzer, Amblin |publisher=Deadline |date=2013-10-04 |accessdate=2015-02-19 |archive-date=2014-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208083323/http://www.deadline.com/2013/10/nbc-developing-comedy-based-on-movie-the-money-pit-with-justin-spitzer-amblin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但该项目后来被搁置。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=https://deadline.com/2014/03/nbc-comedy-pilot-money-pit-pushed-697253/ |title=NBC Comedy Pilot ‘Money Pit’ Pushed |publisher=Deadline |date=2014-03-11 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |archive-date=2015-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926235314/http://deadline.com/2014/03/nbc-comedy-pilot-money-pit-pushed-697253/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

